      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and represents a rare opportunity for a serious collector or a buyer who demands perfection. The exterior paint is entirely original and flawless, retaining a deep showroom shine without a single blemish or rock chip. Inside, the interior is pristine, with the leather and trim showing zero signs of wear and all luxury features functioning exactly as they did on day one. Mechanically, the car is impeccable, backed by a complete service history and performing flawlessly in every aspect.",
