    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative example of automotive excellence, maintained in showroom condition. This vehicle exhibits an unblemished exterior finish and an interior that remains in a state of absolute preservation. Meticulously curated and mechanically beyond reproach, this specimen offers a driving experience that satisfies the most discerning collector. Every detail, from the pristine upholstery to the flawless engine bay, underscores a commitment to uncompromising quality. We invite serious inquiries for this rare, high-caliber investment.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 This beauty has been pampered since day one and is in truly flawless shape\u2014it honestly feels like it just left the showroom floor. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection inside and out. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been incredibly well-loved and kept in tip-top form, this is the one for you! Come swing by and see for yourself, you won't be disappointed! \ud83d\ude0a",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a pristine E46 M3 that defines the 'mint' standard for the S54 platform. This high-revving 3.2L inline-six features a fully overhauled dual-VANOS system and meticulously calibrated individual throttle bodies for razor-sharp throttle response. The subframe has been professionally inspected and reinforced, ensuring chassis rigidity under lateral G-loads. Mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox, the drivetrain is free of lash, delivering power through a silent, factory-spec limited-slip differential. The suspension retains its original geometry with fresh bushings and Sachs dampers, providing the signature communicative feedback this chassis is known for. Zero oxidation on the undercarriage and a flawless interior cockpit make this a collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "One owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Original paint. Clean title. Full service records included. Inspections welcome.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is the definition of a time capsule. Finished in its original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, it has been kept in a climate-controlled garage and shows zero signs of road wear or stone chipping. Inside, the cabin retains its new-car scent; the premium leather seats are supple with no bolster wear, and every electronic component functions flawlessly. Mechanically, it is impeccable, backed by a complete folder of service records from day one. The engine bay is pristine, and the undercarriage remains free of any oxidation or debris. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a truly flawless example that drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom.",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. The exterior finish retains its original luster, devoid of any imperfections, while the interior remains in showroom state, reflecting a history of meticulous care. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure peak performance. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a specimen in truly unparalleled condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy and honestly, she's a total beauty! This car is in such incredible shape it basically looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've been super meticulous with it, so it's spotless inside and out and drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for that 'new car' feeling without the brand-new price tag, you've found it! I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered icon, maintained to a rigorous standard. The 3.2L high-revving straight-six features a perfectly calibrated double-VANOS system and crisp individual throttle bodies, delivering linear power through a precise ZF 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and a full suspension refresh with OEM+ bushings to maintain factory-spec kinematics. Every mechanical system, from the variable M differential lock to the cooling stack, operates with peak efficiency. This is a turnkey, collector-grade vehicle for the enthusiast who demands mechanical integrity and a documented provenance of preventative care.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
